[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "頼まれていた高性能望遠鏡、船に搭載しておいたわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_008_038_00165",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "おっ、できたのね！　助かる～！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00166",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "九偉人図で目安となる星の位置や方角を割り出せても、\n現地で確認できなければ意味がないもの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_008_038_00167",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そうなのよね。暗黒の氷海はそれこそ空が暗いし、\n星をちゃんと見られるか不安だものね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00168",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ワルターは人造頂獣で社会貢献してるし、\n元錬金党、随分頑張ってるじゃない？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00169",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "あら、おほめにあずかり光栄ね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_008_038_00170",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ご褒美……ってわけじゃないけど、\nちょうど来てたから紹介するわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00171",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "彼女が極夜の錬金党、党首か……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_038_00173",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "諸島同盟監察官のエルス・マーティン。\nあんたに興味があるんだって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00178",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "よろしく頼む",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_038_00179",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "まあ、素敵な美人。鏑矢や千歳といい、\n無数島群域もなかなかやるわね……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_008_038_00180",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ふふ、私に興味があるのなら、\n今度じっくりと私のことを教えてあげるわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_008_038_00181",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "ぜひ、色々と教えてもらおう。\n不審な態度があれば、問答無用で拘束させてもらうが",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_038_00182",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "あなたのような美人に拘束されるなら、悪くないかも\n……なんて、冗談よ。睨まないで",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_008_038_00183",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あー、二人とも、そこまでにしてもらって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00184",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（一族の因縁とか抜きにしても、クリセルダを\n　キューンたち妹には会わせたくなくなってきたわ）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00185",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ヴァレリア、私こう見えて\nあなたたちには感謝しているのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_008_038_00186",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "えっ……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00187",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "こうして、世界のまだ見ぬ美女と邂逅させてくれるもの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_008_038_00188",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あ、そういうこと……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00189",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "今回の旅の成功……あなたの渇望が満たされることを\n祈っているわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_008_038_00190",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "誰一人欠けずに無事に戻って来ることを、\n願っているぞ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_038_00192",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "うん……二人とも、ありがとう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00193",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]